Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 查询/list => 成功
GET {{baseUrl}}/app/language/list
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 新增AppLanguageController => 成功
POST {{baseUrl}}/app/language
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
