{
  "id": 1,
  "name": "更新后的名称"
}

### 删除AppLanguageController => 成功
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/app/language/1,2,3
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 执行删除/{ids} => 成功
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/app/language/{ids}
